                content: "To: rafi@email.com\nSubject: My preparation for the upcoming HSC examination.\n\nDear Rafi,\nTake my cordial love. I received your email yesterday. You wanted to know about my preparation for the upcoming HSC examination. \n\nMy preparation is going very well. I have already completed the syllabus for all my subjects. Now, I am purely focusing on revision. I was a bit weak in English and Physics, but with the help of my teachers, I have overcome those difficulties. I am solving previous years' board questions and giving model tests at home to manage my time better. I study for about 10-12 hours a day. \n\nPlease pray for me so that I can achieve a brilliant result. Let me know about your preparation too. Give my regards to your parents.\n\nYours lovingly,\nAsif"
